%% FMS Guardrails Orchestrator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ / mTLS
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>TLS/mTLS
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS/mTLS
    participant LLM as TGIS / caikit-nlp<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>TLS/mTLS
    participant OpenAI as vLLM / OpenAI<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS/mTLS

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 1: Classification with Text Generation (Unary)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC, Cert-based auth
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content safety detection
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch->>LLM: GenerationService.Generate<br/>gRPC, Cert-based auth
    LLM-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>Output detection
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: Classification + Generation response

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 2: Chat Completions with Detection (Streaming)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Header passthrough
    Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions (SSE)<br/>Cert-based auth
    loop Streaming chunks
        OpenAI-->>Orch: SSE chunk
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Chunk detection
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection result
        Orch-->>Client: SSE chunk (filtered)
    end

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 3: Streaming Content Detection (ND-JSON)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>ND-JSON stream
    loop ND-JSON lines
        Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC streaming
        Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content detection
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection result
        Orch-->>Client: ND-JSON detection response
    end
